```
Executes TVM instruction "HASHCU" or "HASHSU". It computes the representation hash of a given argument and returns it as a 256-bit unsigned integer. For string and bytes it computes hash of the tree of cells, which contains data, but not data itself. See sha256 to count hash of data.

